        "text": "This massive tower shield (Hardness 5, HP 20, BT 10) is crafted from the toughest steel. It\u2019s not ideal for single combat, but it can be used to defend soldiers during a siege. While this shield is raised, you gain resistance to damage from siege weapons equal to half this shield\u2019s Hardness.",
